OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FLiam, from Glossop, suffered from
OL,7,Fanxiety and when he visited his GP
OL,8,Fwith chest pains he was told they were
OL,9,Fcaused by stress.
OL,11,FAfter nine months of worsening
OL,12,Fsymptoms he was diagnosed in August
OL,13,F2020 with advanced lung cancer which
OL,14,Fhad spread to his spine, liver and
OL,15,Flymph nodes.
OL,17,FMr Handley, and his Liam's mother
OL,18,FLynn, are now backing the campaign by
OL,19,FRoy Castle to end the focus on the
OL,20,Flabels.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
