OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FScans showed his cancer was growing
OL,7,Fagain and he died in October that
OL,8,Fyear, aged 37.
OL,10,FThe foundation estimates there are
OL,11,Fabout 48,500 people diagnosed with
OL,12,Flung cancer every year in the UK, with
OL,13,Fabout a third of cases unrelated to
OL,14,Fsmoking.
OL,16,FAccording to Mr Handley, the fact Liam
OL,17,Fwas a non-smoker "clouded the doctors'
OL,18,Fview".
OL,26,@yD@ROUzD@EO]
