OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FHe said: "We can only think that the
OL,7,Flabel of non-smoker worked against
OL,8,FLiam.
OL,10,F"The fact that he didn't smoke clouded
OL,11,Fthe doctor's view, so lung cancer was
OL,12,Fnever considered. Now we're left with
OL,13,Fso many questions and his children
OL,14,Fwill grow up without their dad."
OL,16,FRoy Castle Chief Executive Paula
OL,17,FChadwick added: "The sooner lung
OL,18,Fcancer is caught, the more treatment
OL,19,Foptions ` including curative treatment
OL,20,F` a person has.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUvD@`O]yD@QOU
