PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1730723427
OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"So, when we hear a story like Liam's,
OL,7,Fwhere there were clearly missed
OL,8,Fopportunities to diagnose earlier,
OL,9,Fit's vital we understand what went
OL,10,Fwrong."
OL,12,FThe charity's Let Go Of The Labels
OL,13,Fcampaign is calling for an end to
OL,14,Fterms such as smoker and never-smoker
OL,15,Fwhen it comes to lung cancer diagnosis
OL,16,Fand treatment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
