OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1730723427
OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"Lung cancer is still so intrinsically
OL,7,Flinked to smoking but the reality is
OL,8,Fanyone can get this disease,
OL,9,Fregardless of if they have smoked or
OL,10,Fnot," Ms Chadwick said.
OL,12,F"The more people we spoke to, the more
OL,13,Fwe recognised that labels like smoker
OL,14,Fand non-smoker were having a direct
OL,15,Fimpact on how quickly people were
OL,16,Fbeing diagnosed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
