CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1730723427
OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"If a person has smoked, they can feel
OL,7,Fmore reluctant to seek help because
OL,8,Fthey feel ashamed or guilty, or their
OL,9,Fsymptoms are directly attributed to
OL,10,Fsmoking.
OL,12,F"Meanwhile, if someone hasn't smoked,
OL,13,Fthey often aren't referred as quickly
OL,14,Ffor tests as they could have been
OL,15,Fbecause they don't fit the idea of who
OL,16,Fwe expect to have lung cancer."
OL,18,FDave Marcus, from Cheshire, was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with lung cancer in November
OL,20,F2021, when he was 54.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@_O]
