PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1730723427
OL,3,CNon-smoker status 'worked against' dad
OL,4,Cbefore lung cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"I was so focused on the fact that I
OL,7,Fhad never smoked that I,
OL,8,Funintentionally, ignored the clearest
OL,9,Fof warning signs ` a persistent cough.
OL,11,F"It's definitely time we stop thinking
OL,12,Fabout lung cancer in this way. I am
OL,13,Fproof that it can happen to anyone and
OL,14,Fcatching it early means there's life
OL,15,Fafter lung cancer."
OL,17,FMs Chadwick added: "We need to do
OL,18,Feverything we can to ensure everyone
OL,19,Fwith lung cancer is diagnosed as
OL,20,Fquickly as possible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@SO]yD@TOU
